  "text": "Found 7 deprecated DataStream API classes in the Flink codebase under flink-streaming-java/src/. These include I/O format classes, source functions, sink functions, and timestamp extractors:\n\n1. **TextInputFormat** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextInputFormat.java) - An input format for reading text files. Deprecated with @Deprecated annotation. Recommended replacement: Use FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink.\n\n2. **TextOutputFormat** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextOutputFormat.java) - An output format for writing text files. Deprecated with @Deprecated annotation. Recommended replacement: Use FLIP-27 FileSource and Sink-V2 FlinkSink.\n\n3. **AscendingTimestampExtractor** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/timestamps/AscendingTimestampExtractor.java) - A timestamp assigner and watermark generator for streams with monotonously ascending timestamps. Deprecated with @Deprecated annotation.\n\n4. **DiscardingSink** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/sink/legacy/DiscardingSink.java) - A legacy sink function that ignores all elements. Deprecated in JavaDoc. Recommended replacement: Use org.apache.flink.streaming.api.functions.sink.v2.DiscardingSink.\n\n5. **DataGeneratorSource** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/source/datagen/DataGeneratorSource.java) - A legacy data generator source function. Deprecated in JavaDoc. Recommended replacement: Use org.apache.flink.connector.datagen.source.DataGeneratorSource.\n\n6. **TwoPhaseCommitSinkFunction** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/sink/legacy/TwoPhaseCommitSinkFunction.java) - A legacy base class for sinks implementing exactly-once semantics using two-phase commit. Deprecated in JavaDoc. Recommended replacement: Use org.apache.flink.api.connector.sink2.Sink.\n\n7. **StreamingFileSink** (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/sink/filesystem/legacy/StreamingFileSink.java) - A legacy sink that writes to filesystem with bucketing and checkpointing support. Deprecated in JavaDoc. Recommended replacement: Use org.apache.flink.connector.file.sink.FileSink.\n\nAll deprecated classes are located in the Flink streaming module and represent legacy APIs that have been superseded by newer connector and sink interfaces introduced in later Flink versions (particularly FLIP-27 and Sink V2 APIs)."
